rangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"text":"A class which wraps all ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"component  tokens of bar","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBarComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"code":"BarComponentTokens","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to expose the component tokens for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bar"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" through any ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Bar"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors ("},{"code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProviders","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":"), borders (from ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and effects (from ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllEffectSemanticTokensProvider"},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebarcomponenttokensprovider","title":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"Theme Orange","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"type":"topic","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/AllOpacitySemanticTokensProvider":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Something which provides all semantic tokens of opacity"}],"role":"symbol","title":"AllOpacitySemanticTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/allopacitysemantictokensprovider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllOpacitySemanticTokensProvider","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"AllOpacitySemanticTokensProvider"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier